<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url("background3.jpg");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1px blue;
    }

    .alert {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .alert-success {
      background-color: rgb(50, 205, 50);
      color: white;
    }

    .alert-error {
      background-color: rgb(255, 69, 58);
      color: white;
    }

    .container1 {
      position: fixed;
      left: 50px;
      top: 150px;
      color: white;
    }

    .container2 {
      position: fixed;
      left: 300px;
      top: 150px;
      color: white;
      width: 300px;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .video {
      position: fixed;
      left: 700px;
      top: 150px;
      color: white;
      width: 300px;
    }

    .wanttogo {
      position: fixed;
      left: 30px;
      top: 470px;
    }
  </style>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Annapurna Circuit</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    crossorigin="anonymous" />
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark mb-2">
    <a class="navbar-brand" style="color: rgb(191, 255, 161)">Annapurna Circuit</a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
      aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
      <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto"></ul>
      <form method="POST" action='/searchresults' class="form-inline my-2 my-lg-0">
        <input class="form-control mr-sm-2" name="Search" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-success my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit">Search</button>
                 
      </form>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Success or Error Messages -->
  <% if (success) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-success">
      <%= success %>
    </div>
    <% } %>
      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-error">
          <%= error %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

          <div class="container1">
            <img id="image" src="/annapurna.png" width="193" height="300" />
          </div>
          <div class="container2">
            Annapurna Circuit has been voted as the best long-distance trek in the
            world, as it combined a wide variety of climate zones from tropics at 600m
            above sea level to the arctic at 5416m above sea level at the Thorong La
            pass and cultural variety from Hindu villages at the low foothills to the
            Tibetan culture of Manang.
          </div>

          <div class="wanttogo">
            <form method="POST" action="/add-to-wanttogo">
              <input type="hidden" name="location" value="Annapurna" />
              <button id="wanttogo" class="btn btn-secondary ml-3">
                Add to Want-to-Go List
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="video">
            <iframe width="480" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zp72WjMVhTQ?si=Zm8vP2E_J3ervcjq"
              title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
</body>

</html>